item.description:
Venez nous rejoindre pour une soirée décontractée ... venez discuter avec nous !



UPDATE "BIS": We will meet at the *new* Kar-Min, which will celebrate its grand reopening this day with a free appetizer for each table! Come taste a dish from the updated menu, if you wish, and join us for a bit of conversation.

**Eric, the new owner, says that you will not be obliged to order, so please come even if you don't want to eat with us.**
item.how_to_find_us: Look for the red and white French Meetup sign on the table!
